    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly flawless shape and drives like a cloud. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to be so happy. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
